<li><a href="Brazil" title="Brazil">Brazil</a>, 1974–1983, 1984–2000, 2000–2006, 2008–present;</li>
<li>Australia, 1980–present;</li>
</ul>
</td>
<td align="left" valign="top">
<ul>
<li>South Africa, 1985–present;</li>
<li>Spain, 2006–present;</li>
<li>Netherlands, 1964–1996; 2011–present;</li>
</ul>
