<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Mad_(magazine)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: Past foreign editions">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Past_foreign_editions">Past foreign editions</span></h3>
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="multicol" style="background:transparent; width:100%;">
<tr>
